thread.title: Sarah

author: Sarah
title: Sarah
text: Shortly after purchasing my investment unit I moved real estate agents to Nelson Alexander as the original agent was having trouble leasing the property. After 1 week my property had been leased which was a huge relief after being vacate for 6 weeks prior. I find Daniel Carusi my property manager to be very professional, prompt with delivering a service and reliable to give good advice and answer any questions I have. I have just released my property after 5 years and he was very helpful supporting me to arrange maintenace and liasing professionally between the leaving tenant and I thanks.
